signature. The other channels do not show any\nsignificant departure from Gaussianity with our estimator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2002 18:07:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 Oct 2002 18:55:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
