er plane (i.e. outside the infinitely many Arnol'd tongues)\nfractally nonlinear. 2) `Negative Response': Inside certain regions with an\napparently fractal boundary the current J and the bias b have opposite signs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jul 2002 20:28:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Jul 2002 12:25:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-26"}
